          "text": "俺，姓庞名德字令名。只因曹仁襄阳败阵，魏王挂于禁为帅，命俺以为先行。\n俺自备皮榇一口，此去援军，定与关羽决一死战。远远望见元帅来也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、四上手、于禁同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "庞德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见元帅！"
        },
        {
          "character": "于禁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人马可齐？"
        },
        {
          "character": "庞德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俱已齐备。"
        },
        {
          "character": "于禁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "起兵襄阳去者！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "庞德→于禁",
          "turns": 2
        },
        {
          "edge": "于禁→庞德",
          "turns": 1
        }
      ],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
