    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "众将",
        "关羽",
        "四上手",
        "庞德"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、马童、庞德、关羽同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，马前来的敢是庞德？"
        },
        {
          "character": "庞德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "然！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "庞将军！关某威名，尔岂不知？若肯归降，关某有爱将之癖，饶你不死。"
        },
        {
          "character": "庞德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "关羽！某奉魏王之命，来解樊城之围。今日阵前相会，倒要看看你的刀法如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "关羽马前，未遇三合之将。"
        },
        {
          "character": "庞德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看刀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖吹打〗。关羽、庞德同对刀。于禁、马良双上，摇旗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "庞德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，关羽你敢是怯战？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你营先自鸣金，何言关某怯战？\n众将官！"
        },
        {
          "character": "众将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "收兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽、马童、众将同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "庞德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住。某与关羽，大战一百余合，眼见关羽气力不足。不知元帅为何鸣金收兵？\n众将官！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四上手",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "庞德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回营。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
