    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "于禁",
        "庞德",
        "龙套"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、于禁同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "于禁",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "统领七军身为重，岂容庞德立头功。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（庞德、四上手同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "庞德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见元帅！"
        },
        {
          "character": "于禁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "庞将军辛苦了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "庞德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "元帅，适才关羽阵前，力已不支，正要擒他下马，元帅为何鸣金收兵？"
        },
        {
          "character": "于禁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个……某恐关羽有诈，故而鸣金。"
        },
        {
          "character": "庞德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "元帅，依某之见趁此锐气，统领七军，冲入敌营，以解樊城之围。"
        },
        {
          "character": "于禁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎！临行之时，魏王曾传谕旨，告诫我等不可轻敌。依本帅之见，只宜谨守，\n切莫贪功。"
        },
        {
          "character": "庞德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "元帅！魏王有言，可取则取，不可取则宜谨守。今日一战，胜负即见，理当进\n取。何言庞某贪功？"
        },
        {
          "character": "于禁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "本帅遵奉谕旨，早有成算在心。就将七路大军，移往樊城之北，依山下寨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "庞德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊？"
        },
        {
          "character": "于禁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "庞德听令！"
        },
        {
          "character": "庞德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在！"
        },
        {
          "character": "于禁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命你带领本部人马，屯扎山谷之内，无令不可进兵，本帅自有奇谋破敌。"
        },
        {
          "character": "庞德",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令！带马。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（庞德、四下手同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "于禁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将官！"
        },
        {
          "character": "龙套",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "于禁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将人马扎在山旁，截断大路，阻挡关羽，并防庞德擅自进兵。就此移营者。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（于禁、众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
