    {
      "scene_index": 5,
      "label": "第五场",
      "characters_present": [
        "众将",
        "关平",
        "关羽",
        "周仓",
        "大骂庞德尔好威风",
        "尔好煞气"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马童、周仓引关羽同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周将。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周仓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "传令下去，人不可卸甲，马不可离鞍，明日五鼓天明，大战庞德。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周仓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咋，咋，咋！\n三军的，人不可卸甲，马不可离鞍，明日五鼓天明，大战那庞德。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众人 （内同白） 啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马童下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "周仓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "传令已毕。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "起过一旁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周仓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "收了刀枪卷了旗，两下鸣金各自归。强中自有强中手，庞德刀法世间稀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周仓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "庞德好刀法！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恨庞德英勇无敌，"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刀来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周仓交过刀。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刀哇！想你过关斩将，何等威风。今日小小庞德，战他不过，好不气煞人也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "纵有青龙刀要尔何用。\n阵前逞能轻视俺关某——\n赤兔马要尔还何用。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大骂庞德尔好威风，尔好煞气、周仓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只怕那庞德，明日再来讨战。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那庞德明日里若来讨战——"
        },
        {
          "character": "周仓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待俺周仓会他一会。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "周仓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "某与少将军一同出马。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗯？"
        },
        {
          "character": "周仓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我等随定君侯，杀他个三马连环。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哼！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三马连环战庞德，岂不羞惭！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关平上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关平",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "于禁迁移营，进帐报军情。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关平进帐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关平",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启禀爹爹：今有于禁将七路军马，移在山口扎营。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有这等事？\n关平、周将随我查看者。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（粉蝶儿） 离却宝帐，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽向下场望。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "关羽 （粉蝶儿） 出营房敌情查防，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽向上场望。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "关羽 （粉蝶儿） 雾腾腾杀气弥漫，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽向中场望。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "关羽 （粉蝶儿） 上山冈仔细观望。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽正场高望。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "关羽 （粉蝶儿） 白茫茫一带襄江，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（水声。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "关羽 （粉蝶儿） 又听得水声沧浪。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（七军同上，过场，同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "周仓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哇呀呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "关羽 （粉蝶儿） 魏营中移营盘军号喧嚷，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "猛然间计上胸膛。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "擒庞德和七军尽赴汪洋。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周仓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回营！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽、周仓、关平同下山，关羽归座。众将同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关平",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爹爹为何发笑？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我笑的是庞德恃勇，于禁无谋。七路大军，屯扎在罾口川低洼之处。鱼入罾口，\n岂能久乎？某略施小计，管叫他全军尽没。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周仓、关平",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "君侯之计如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "沿江决口，水淹七军。\n周将听令！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周仓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咋。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命你将树伐倒，造成木排，带领五百水手，生擒庞德。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周仓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周仓下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "关平听令！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关平",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命你带领一千人马，准备沙囊土袋，去至襄江，将上下流水堵塞。只等江水暴\n涨，将近上流土袋撤去，决破堤口，然后水面杀敌。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关平",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关平下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将官！"
        },
        {
          "character": "众将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "全军人马，连夜移驻高阜之上准备船只，尽灭七军去者！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽、众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
